cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.IR 

This paper deals with machine learning methods for text classification of social media posts related to mental health. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also uses automated machine learning tools, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with data mining and prediction, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
